stream nvidia-smi: 

$ /usr/lib/wsl/lib/nvidia-smi dmon -s pucmt  # power, GPU%, mem%, clocks, temp


nvtop interactive TUI:

$ sudo add-apt-repository multiverse -y && sudo apt update
$ sudo apt install -y nvtop
$ nvtop


lightweight CLI:

$ pip install --user gpustat
$ ~/.local/bin/gpustat --watch 1

or in venv:

$ pip install gpustat
$ gpustat --watch 1
